---

### 3. User Authentication System

#### Register Feature
- User can register with email and password
- Password is securely hashed using bcrypt
- Duplicate email check added

#### Login Feature
- User login with email & password
- Password verified using bcrypt
- JWT token generated after successful login

---

### 4. JWT Authentication
- Token-based authentication implemented
- Protected routes created
- Only logged-in users can access secure APIs

---

### 5. Course Module
- Course table created
- Course list API implemented
- Protected course access added (JWT required)

